@drcat123
Wrong, it is the 21st episode (S06BE08) in the AIRED order.

The actual number of the episode is 15.

@drcat123
This being episode 15 has absolutely nothing to do with wikipedia... That is what episode this is... EVERYWHERE. 6ACV15 is the official production code; it is officially episode 15. They just chose to broadcast it in a different order.

Also, you're still wrong, can you not read or something? If you use Wikipedia or the episode gudie spifkitten99 posted, you can see that Episode 23 was last week (all the presidents' heads) yet it was aired as episode 20 (S06BE07). Episode 21 was July 21st (yo leela leela) and was aired as episode 19 (S06BE06).

@spifkitten99
The Wikipedia has all the info on that guide, and more, and is more organized, and more accurate. By accurate I mean it lists the episodes by their official tv name, such as this episode being S06BE08 (Season 6B Episode 8). Either way, both guides are pretty much the same.

As for opposing ASAP release so strongly, even going as far as saying "ASAP has not yet produced any videos in anything even close to decent quality." is clearly just your opinion. Which is wrong, because clearly this is pretty decent quality. Sure it isn't MAXIMUM SUPER BEST ULTRA CRYSTAL CLEAR quality... but that would make it High quality, not "decent".
